{"tid":265683,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"IMF：加拿大樓市嚴重「失衡」 (06:01)","createTime":"2017-05-31T22:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T06:25:13.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15fe35d3b797b1af733be9c67c94892c6c8986ab","tid":265683,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T22:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170601/img/20170601060115fi_p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170601%2Fimg%2F20170601060115fi_p1.jpg&h=398af2b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年3月，多倫多樓價年化增長率為28%。<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=Ii6SpWfcqDH85TvitJNNTJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=948836ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】據外媒，國際貨幣基金組織(IMF)周三發表報告指，加拿大房地產市場嚴重「失衡」，恐將對加拿大經濟產生巨大風險。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，加拿大家庭面臨巨大的償債壓力，特別是加拿大和多倫多，對於首次置業的買家而言，這已經是社會問題了。今年3月，多倫多樓價年化增長率為28%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170601/20170601060115fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170601%2F20170601060115fi.html&d=Ii6SpWfcqDH85TvitJNNTJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=728b915c\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170601/20170601060115fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"78796a5c6305b1cac04b8a6920546ad3b7443c56","tid":265683,"uid":44559,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T23:32:28.000Z","msg":"香港笑而不語"},{"pid":"191b6d7bf80730d6122284866698c891ac3e5d1a","tid":265683,"uid":51933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:58:32.000Z","msg":"IMF見識少<br />\n望下香港幾平衡"},{"pid":"a058748ce104691152cfbeebcc1fb9d891da8c72","tid":265683,"uid":56188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T02:21:04.000Z","msg":"又係紅色資金炒起"},{"pid":"0e9ff751b9432ac166d625ae5d4771f0b1bc0020","tid":265683,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T02:51:41.000Z",